*******************************************************************************
1.1.50
*******************************************************************************
2005-06-22  monkeyiq  <monkeyiq@users.sourceforge.net>

	Ability to mount evolution email and contacts,
	Native PostgreSQL mounting support,
	Improvements to Shell::acquireContext(),
	better whitespace handling in parseSeperatedList(),
	as-text filter for Word files,
	New is-dir-try-automounting EA which will attempt
	to automount a file before reporting that it is not
	a directory,
	New size EA fallback which generates its value by
	reading the byte contents of a file,
	fca:// formal concepts now export their object-id as EA,
	various speed improvements to FCA engine.

*******************************************************************************
1.1.46 is below.
*******************************************************************************
ChangeLog
	Adding files to PostgreSQL EA index is now significantly faster.
	PostgreSQL EA indexer no longer does an analyse after adding files.
	Memory leak fix in RPM EA generators.
	Some fd leaks fixed in the as-text EA generators.
	Bug that caused a segv in the jpeg EA generator for some jpeg files fixed.
	language-human EA now uses as-text EA to dig into pdf files.
	Better relative path resolution.
	Added another optional MIME sniffing engine using libmagic.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
